        "beginner": "Rock layers are like a stack of pancakes; the bottom pancake was cooked first (older) than the top one.",
        "intermediate": "The lower stratum was deposited first. Therefore, the reptile fossil is older than the mammal fossil found above it.",
        "advanced": "Relative dating via stratigraphy provides a sequential order of fossil occurrence. Absolute dating would be needed to determine the exact number of years difference.",
